      "date": "2019-07-18 16:27:16.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nYingjin,\n\nI believe this specific patch was replaced by another one - Could you abandon it and any others that were similarly replaced?  (It's still showing up in lists of related changes in Gerrit)",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
