        "subject": "LU-10918 pcc: auto RO-PCC caching when open files",
        "message": "LU-10918 pcc: auto RO-PCC caching when open files\n\nDuring the file open, if the file is being opened with O_RDONLY\nflags, and the file matches the predefined rule, it will be\nprefetched and attached into RO-PCC automatically.\n\nSigned-off-by: Qian Yingjin <qian@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: Ib2c2ab51d67aed84eb7676c8df191faa33dfad39\n"
